                            <comment id="17228655" author="edimitrova" created="Mon, 9 Nov 2020 15:10:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Transaction files on JBOD may become out of sync, that is lines are not in the same order.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To prevent that we synchronize LogTransaction.java&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/commit/7d4007e942202809925b0d715bc519fd8f7d5ba0&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;trunk &lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/483/workflows/0fc7c223-7b2f-450a-9697-36cb2f295ad1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;JAVA8 CI &lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/483/workflows/2e4ca8af-217f-4778-8da9-064b24c2fbf4&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;JAVA11 CI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/commit/bbf11d406dc88bc646cad45c4dfb8cf7135ff72c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;3.11 &lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/482/workflows/5b9f1098-9b79-4477-9ca9-ef9ff8c57e84&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/commit/6b72d5ebe82e7ed031708a1ad4cd45f6c76ca525&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;3.0 &lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/481/workflows/3b4e63f5-5f09-4520-8e0c-764410febec3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CI &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No new failures.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=brandon.williams&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;brandon.williams&quot;&gt;brandon.williams&lt;/a&gt;, can you, please, review?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17229388" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 10 Nov 2020 17:32:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17236337" author="edimitrova" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2020 17:52:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=maedhroz&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;maedhroz&quot;&gt;maedhroz&lt;/a&gt;&#160;pointed that I missed the synchronization for&#160;LogTransaction#untrackNew()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I corrected it for 3.0 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/commit/e5241dfa3c097d6078f95823272a1e1c73c00002&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. This could be merged to the rest of the branches.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Not sure whether we need full CI run again&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=maedhroz&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;maedhroz&quot;&gt;maedhroz&lt;/a&gt;&#160;and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=psynix%40t-online.de&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;psynix@t-online.de&quot;&gt;psynix@t-online.de&lt;/a&gt;, can you review, please? And thank you for reaching out, appreciate it! &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17236359" author="jmeredithco" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2020 18:24:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on the code. No deadlock issues with callers holding different locks that I could see.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve cherry-picked it and am going to run it through CI locally against trunk.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17236446" author="jmeredithco" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2020 21:20:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In-tree tests passed on my cherry-pick for trunk.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17241197" author="edimitrova" created="Tue, 1 Dec 2020 01:57:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=psynix%40t-online.de&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;psynix@t-online.de&quot;&gt;psynix@t-online.de&lt;/a&gt;, do I understand correctly that no full CI run is expected and I can ask &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=brandon.williams&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;brandon.williams&quot;&gt;brandon.williams&lt;/a&gt; Brandon for this ninja fix commit, if he doesn&apos;t have any concerns?&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17242586" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 2 Dec 2020 18:17:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ninja&apos;d the fix and correct changes entry in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/2bcbd92a25c420b30cc8cc0eb8b266d9889ea973&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/2bcbd92a25c420b30cc8cc0eb8b266d9889ea973&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
